collection.name: DystoPunks
collection.description:
Welcome to a tech-filled dystopian future where only **2077 Punks** survived.

**DystoPunks** is a utility-focused Cyberpunk-themed NFT project that allows holders to generate a utility token called **$CREDS**, mint [Dystolab Crates](https://opensea.io/collection/dystolab-crates) and use it in the **Dystoverse**.

Metaverse Avatars: [DystoPunks VX](https://opensea.io/collection/dystopunks-vx)

[Website](https://dystopunks.net/) **|** [Discord](https://discord.gg/DystoPunks) **|** [Medium](https://dystopunks.medium.com/) **|** [Twitter](https://twitter.com/DystoPunks)

Where it all started: 

[DystoPunks V1](https://opensea.io/collection/dystopunks-v1) **|** [DystoPunks 3D](https://opensea.io/collection/dystopunks-3d) **|** [CyberCrocz](https://opensea.io/collection/cybercrocz) **|** [CryptoCheems](https://opensea.io/collection/cryptocheems)
